<measure quantity="1" unit="chapter">
<num value="1">一</num>卷</measure>
<pc>（</pc>大學士英廉家藏本<pc>）</pc>國朝潘鼎珪撰<pc>。</pc>鼎珪字子登<pc>，</pc>晉江人<pc>。</pc>是編成於康熙<measure quantity="27" unit="years">
<num value="27">二十七</num>年</measure>
